gram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Featuring in the opening ceremony is generally a source of great pride and excitement for athletes, who get the chance to represent their country and walk alongside fellow Olympians all dreaming of taking home coveted medals.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"great pride\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow Olympians\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"coveted medals\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Team GB star Evans has no plans to attend and says her decision is ultimately for 'performance reasons'.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999840863049255, \"rank\": 1.4253004899949887e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\", \"score\": 0.9225913526778976, \"rank\": 0.08390350406171782, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no plans\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"performance reasons\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This will be my fourth major championships and I have not yet been 