m\": 1540, \"to\": 1546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And that then means you go, \\\"no\\\" [to the opening ceremony].\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because, obviously there is a lot of standing about and a lot of waiting.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"waiting\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sorry to burst the bubble.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bubble\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are standing for like hours and hours and hours to get in the right place so they can parade you in at exactly the right moment and that's not good for performance, basically.'\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"the right place\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly the right moment\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what she plans to do on Friday night instead, Evans added: 'I think we are going to do something on the evening, we will probably go for dinner in the [opening ceremony] kit as like a nod to it, if you like.'\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\", \"score\": 0.9225913526778976, \"rank\": 0.08390350406171782, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBab